This is a work in progress.  Unfortunately, it's only half-baked at the
moment.  Eventually it'll work, I promise.

NAME
    wanfaild - Monitor WAN links and provide failover

DESCRIPTION
    wanfaild will monitor one or more WAN links and provide failover
    support.

SYNOPSIS
    wanfaild [options]

     Options:
       --conf       -c      Specify configuration file
       --help       -h      Help message

     Long options:
       --version            Print the version number

AUTHOR
    Steven Pritchard <steve@kspei.com>

